        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>After 15 min, remove the tray with the vegetables from the oven and open up the parcel</p><p>Add your <strong>sesame oil</strong> and sprinkle over your <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven and cook for a further 5-6 mins or until the vegetables are tender – this is your <strong>sesame roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646746946244-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
