    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>five-spice roasted chicken</strong> with the <strong>sesame roasted veg </strong>and <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>plum sauce </strong>over the chicken</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
